    <description>The S-ICD System is an implantable technology that uses a subcutaneous pulse generator and subcutaneous electrode system to treat ventricular tachyarrhythmias. The S-ICD System consists of the SQ-RX pulse generator (Model 1010), the Q-TRAK subcutaneous electrode (Model 3010), the Q-TECH programmer (Model 2020), and Q-GUIDE electrode insertion tools (Models 4010 and 4020).</description>
